{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"芊小璇","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM4CzJlG4SDIDuADSIPLBSI3fQIbzM4B81bmVF8d8dic0lp9kwoSlKl4kkSficefGdQSg0vxOBdZeCPRpbSLlnOrsR67x3ozLYJYQ/0","content":"能力：可以满足对方的精神和物质需求<div>匹配：和自己差不多的</div><div>信心：人缘好，在一起舒服</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7789,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492317904000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"王佳","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-15","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AywoaJCYTv4hicL3wib7fApyhLPNJiaroIhefibZ5St8K9AWkmRhDQ3astuE22Q5cDMLXKe5anwROuryia/0","content":"<p>额，作为知根知底的夫妻，用3C模型武装自己还真是很困难，因为一武装就会被发现，被发现就会武装失败。</p><p>我用3C来教我的小堂弟（今年初三）撩妹吧。</p><p>他是个帅气、学习不错、会弹钢琴的小伙子，喜欢文艺和可爱型女孩，但是又比较腼腆。</p><p>能力：首先要展示学习能力，也就是考前十名。其次要爱笑，帅气的人要笑才能吸引女生。再次，了解一些诗词歌赋，不时强说愁。</p><p>匹配：他喜欢文艺和可爱型女生，那么就要投其所好。把上课笔记做好，借给喜欢的女生或者跟人家讨论，同时聊一聊音乐，表明自己的钢琴水平。</p><p>信心：像跟家人一样交往就好。</p><p>呵呵，编不下去了。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7745,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492248797000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Bryce","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoEUMhO4vLWCnI4Q4mvkDusPBDh3XsxUEuQ6Ticu4ZR084FGF6lOUrUZsWMgnKK1squCngsib37KZEib/0","content":"能力：能让你和她一起过上幸福的生活，有这个潜力也算。包括物质和精神上。需要在认识初期就要展现自身价值，生存价值（资产，收入或至少有潜力），繁殖价值（干净的外表，有气色等）<div><br></div><div>匹配：和对方的价值观，兴趣方面需要有一定的重合度。聊天时多从对方角度想想，比如大多数时候，聊白百何出轨话题能延续下去，聊美航赶亚裔下飞机估计就没有然后了。</div><div><br></div><div>信心：穿着得体能带来自信，进而让对方感受到自己的自信。交流时要谈笑风生，不刻意奉承，也别害羞。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7659,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492084145000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"盛夏tl","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-12","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQLZSOLpBibDcibZ6sFXGjaugXibNJwMAvZF35uJNo0TzNd8uGdLrfymhDiav0qNFFCZzEIQIxyrWNEPw/0","content":"这是把3c用于实战啊！用心去关爱另一半。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7603,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492002063000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"浅紫","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-12","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5Qias5Y6BOJq0bibrmkolNJFtbyicK1y9rN41JY4SIw04awshr8lhByygakZc9SVzOfPej1XNTbShq/0","content":"待补充","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7578,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491968315000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"潇洒鳕鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UyLlHC2Q1gMdxzMwDhQicAb4RP8PgibVuS6OEZoCGk0aIWo8mMahY8wu6ic8YFFqdsInJgJAaxbe58CIgsSXQC94U/0","content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">首先，据我所知，男女思考问题的角度大多是不同的，这跟男女大脑结构的差异有关。有没有发现大部分美女的另一半都是相貌平平的？因此我们要充分考虑这种差异，以便能够<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">在找对方需求的时候进行一番</span>深掘。例如不熟悉的男人女人见面时，男人相对更多是外貌协会，认为漂亮的就能够更进一步关注，不好看的嘛多半在内心已经封杀掉，所以建议女方在与男方，见面之前可以适当地化一点妆，选择一件不错的衣服；但是女人则会在相貌普通的基础上更多地注意言谈举止，认为言谈举止达到标准的能够更进一步关注，所以建议男方在与女方见面之前，多准备一些有趣的话题，当然，见面前最好嚼片口香糖。</span><br></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">其次，不管对方是什么样的，与异性见面之前都得先对自己充满信心。在接下来见面的过程中，神态表情、言谈举止等也要让对方感受到这种自信。当然，这里说的是自信而不是自负，万不可表现得太满，以免起到反效果。</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">再次，要想找到好的伴侣，展示自己的能力是不可避免的，那么在交谈的过程中可以适当地在话题当中进行一些展示，当然最有效的办法还是能够在交谈中了解到对方对能力的偏好后再伺机找一些案例来进行充分展示，这样定能事半功倍。</span><br></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7448,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491781065000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"咕咕","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-09","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoAOwic4GNKoz5oR3ECE0v0lAicujK9wBbRPMVWrjBNRath8ZicUnKVKP1TicLlXAlKrf2HJNO0Vv5SH5/0","content":"把话题引到我会做的事上；听懂对方言语背后的需求，显示自己相应匹配的方面有兴趣或擅长；对自己擅长的话题侃侃而谈","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7445,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491751820000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"郭舒简","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-06","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XRibESzncllLeNVVgOoXl3jmKXQT07IR1fYwPRIgiboTXU2tjiaAn3zpZ6cp8iaIvcTMxyrcwRR0P62w/0","content":"3C模型建立更好的情侣关系：<div><br><div>能力</div><div>- 能够经济独立</div><div>- 厨艺还需要修炼</div><div>- 坚持健身，具备健身基础知识</div><div><br></div><div>匹配：他的需求</div><div>- 在他失意的时候给他安慰和鼓励</div><div>- 满足他的大男子主义，夸奖他给他信心</div><div>- 陪他吃喝玩乐，带给他欢乐</div><div>- 有人关心和给予温暖</div><div><br></div><div>信心</div><div>- 知性、体贴、善解人意</div><div>- 开朗、活泼，给生活带来惊喜</div><div>- 智慧，时不时给他好建议</div></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7287,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491469271000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Leo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-05","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSic0ds8BMCibGZ2OUAZx2wvLS7l0JfCujUnFH561QnYtbqvZs2sAcicsmYHVHeJSgYia20o2R8WfC0mn/0","content":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">能力：同理心，观察力，活动策划能力。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">匹配：用同理心满足普遍需求——共情；用观察力满足普遍需求——被认可，用活动策划能力营造约会环境、制定活动内容。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">信心：通过观察了解以及充分准备，将不可控因素降低；活现自我而又不自以为是。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7251,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491397959000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"pro